snippet.title: How to generate Sine Wave in Matlab - Generating a Sine Wave in MATLAB 2017
snippet.description:
How to generate Sine Wave in Matlab - Generating a Sine Wave in MATLAB 2017 

In this Matlab tutorial for beginners, we will see how to generate and plot sine wave in Matlab. For more Matlab tutorials check http://onlineengineers.info

A sine wave or sinusoid is a mathematical curve that describes a smooth repetitive oscillation. It is named after the function sine, of which it is the graph.
